Burney Center : \n The renovated Burney Center includes a 9,300 square foot ballroom with five different space configurations. The facility will seat 500 guests for a banquet and 980 guests auditorium style. The facility includes a large lobby area, two "green" rooms, an events support office, excellent lighting and sound systems, and a spacious catering prep area.
